  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648544994533-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648544994533-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648544994533-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648544994533-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1648544994533-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and grate <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> red onion</strong></p><p>Finely dice the <strong>remaining onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648544997024-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648544997024-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648544997024-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648544997024-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1648544997024-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>beef mince</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>grated onion</strong>, your<strong> garam masala</strong>, <strong>ginger &</strong> <strong>garlic paste </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix thoroughly until fully combined, then shape into 1 sausage shaped kebab per person – this is your <strong>spiced kebab[s]</strong></p><p>Tip: Wet your hands to stop the mince sticking to them!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1648545000081-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
