    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel lengths from the outside of your<strong> cucumber[s]</strong> with a peeler until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Dice the <strong>inner</strong> <strong>stem[s] </strong>of the cucumber</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Combine the <strong>cucumber ribbons</strong>, <strong>chopped mint</strong> and your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>cucumber raita</strong></p>",
