    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the <strong>diced tomato</strong>,<strong> diced cucumber</strong>, <strong>diced red onion </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>kachumber salad</strong></p><p>Put your<strong> naan[s] </strong>in the oven for 3 min or until warmed through</p>",
