    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>To build, spread<strong> </strong>the<strong> cucumber raita </strong>on a <strong>warmed naan</strong>, then top with a <strong>spiced beef kebab</strong>, some <strong>kachumber salad </strong>and a dollop of your <strong>mango chutney</strong> – this is your <strong>Indian-style beef kebab loaded naan</strong></p>",
