      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Indian-style beef kebab loaded naan </strong>with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>remaining kachumber salad</strong> and<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: Fold up the sides of the naan and eat it like a hot dog</p><p>Napkins at the ready, it's about to get messy!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
